        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> est croissante sur <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\([0,1[\\)</span> donc <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(L\\)</span> existe dans <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\([0,+\\infty]\\)</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(L = \\sup\\limits_{[0,1[} f(x)\n              \\ge \\sup\\limits_{[0,1[} \\sum_{n=1}^N x^n\\sin\\frac1{\\sqrt\nn}\n              \\ge \\sum_{n=1}^N \\sin\\frac1{\\sqrt n}  \\Rightarrow  L =\n+\\infty\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
